<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <title>意見ないですMeter</title>
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    </head>
    <body class="container p-1">
        <dl class="row">
            <h1 class="col-sm-6">意見ないです Meter</h1>
                <dd class="col-sm-2">ルーム: <%= name %></dd>
                <ul class="col-sm-4 list-inline" id="members">メンバー: </ul>
        </dl>
    
    <div class="p-2 bd-highlight card flex-fill">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column bd-highlight">

                <h5 class="card-title">ニックネーム</h5>
            <form id="ideaForm" class="input-group mb-2">
                <input id="ideaText" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="あなたのニックネーム">
                <button id="btn" class="btn btn-outline-secondary dropdown-toggle" type="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">おすすめ</button>
                <button id="ideaButton" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" type="submit">決定</button>
                <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-end">
                    <option id="gohan" class="dropdown-item">ご飯🍚</option>
                    <option id="asobi" class="dropdown-item">遊び🎡</option>
                    </ul>
            </form>
            
                <h5 class="card-title" id="willslider">あなたの今のHPは?</h5>
                <p class="fst-italic">メンバーの最小値と距離の近いアイデアは当たる確率が高くなるよ!</p>
                <dl class="p-2 bd-highlight card flex-fill">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                <h1 id="usersInput" class="col-sm-1">😺</h1>
                <input id="willSlider" class="col-sm-8" type="range" min="0" max="100" step="1" >
                <button id="willButton" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" type="button">決定</button>
                </div>
                </dl>
                
                <h5 class="card-title">ニックネームを動かそう!</h5><p class="fst-italic">「意見ある度」が高いほど右に、低いほど左に置こう</p>
                <div id="p5container" class="bd-highlight"></div>　<!-- ←メーターの部分 -->
                
                <div class="text-center">
                <button type="button" id="lotteryButton" class="btn btn-outline-danger">Let's Try to Say!</button>
            </div>
            </div>
                <div id="lotteryResult"></div>    
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    
            



    </body>
        
        <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/p5@1.4.2/lib/p5.js"></script>
        <script>const roomName = "<%= name %>";</script>
        <script src="/sketch.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>